<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MangaDB</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css" />
  </head>
  <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
  <body class="text-center">
    <div
      id="carouselExampleCaptions"
      class="carousel slide"
      data-bs-ride="carousel"
    >
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide-to="0"
          class="active"
          aria-current="true"
          aria-label="Slide 1"
        ></button>
        <button
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide-to="1"
          aria-label="Slide 2"
        ></button>
        <button
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide-to="2"
          aria-label="Slide 3"
        ></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <div class="slide-container">
            <img
              src="https://i.imgur.com/K9nu88w.jpeg"
              class="d-block w-100 slide-image img-fluid"
              alt="..."
            />
            <div class="gradient-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i><span> 1</span>
            <h2>Chainsaw Man</h2>
            <p class="author">TATSUKI FUJIMOTO</p>
            <p>
              Denji, a poor 16-year-old boy who makes a deal with a dog-like
              devil named Pochita and gains the ability to turn parts of his
              body into chainsaws.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="slide-container">
            <img
              src="https://i.imgur.com/DvTK8Au.jpeg"
              class="d-block w-100 slide-image img-fluid"
              alt="..."
            />
            <div class="gradient-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i><span> 2</span>
            <h2>Jujutsu Kaisen</h2>
            <p>GEGE AKUTAMI</p>
            <p>
              Jujutsu Kaisen follows high schooler Yuji Itadori as he joins a
              secret organization to battle curses, malevolent spirits fueled by
              negative human emotions, in a quest to save humanity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="slide-container">
            <img
              src="https://images5.alphacoders.com/606/606284.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100 slide-image img-fluid"
              alt="..."
            />
            <div class="gradient-overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i><span> 3</span>
            <h2>One Piece</h2>
            <p>EIICHIRO ODA</p>
            <p>
              As a child, Monkey D. Luffy was inspired to become a pirate by
              listening to the tales of the buccaneer "Red-Haired" Shanks. But
              Luffy's life changed when he accidentally ate the Gum-Gum Devil
              Fruit and gained the power to stretch like rubber...at the cost of
              never being able to swim again! Years later, still vowing to
              become the king of the pirates, Luffy sets out on his
              adventure...one guy alone in a rowboat, in search of the legendary
              "One Piece," said to be the greatest treasure in the world...
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button
        class="carousel-control-prev"
        type="button"
        data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
        data-bs-slide="prev"
      >
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button
        class="carousel-control-next"
        type="button"
        data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
        data-bs-slide="next"
      >
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="break d-flex" id="explore">
      <h2 class="favorites-text">fan favorites</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="favorites-container">
      <% for(let i=0; i < 14; i++){ %>
      <a href="/manga/<%=manga[i].id; %>"
        ><div class="card" style="width: 12rem">
          <img
            class="card-img-top"
            src="<%= manga[i].img%>"
            alt="<%= manga[i].title %> Cover Art>"
          />
          <div class="card-body d-block">
            <h5 class="card-title"><%=manga[i].title; %></h5>
            <p class="card-subtitle"><%= manga[i].author %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <a
      class="btn btn-danger mb-4"
      href="/collection"
      style="background-color: #ec3b0f"
      >VIEW ALL</a
    >
    <hr />
    <footer>
      <div class="footer">
        <h6>MANGADB Â© 2024</h6>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/44b27bb339.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
